You need the Android SDK installed 
You may need to set ANDROID_HOME in your .bashrc or .bash_profile to point to where your android-sdk lives

To get dependencies and run tests:
	mvn test

To get maven on osx: 
	brew install maven

To deploy to your running android emulator from the command line, use:
mvn android:deploy



Using: android version 14 (specified in POM file)

Please update this readme
I moved the repo to the CapeDevDal organization on github.
